STAT

static font

Titillium Web SemiBold Regular (TitilliumWeb-SemiBold.ttf)

STAT

static font

Variable font must have a STAT table.

No check of STAT table for static fonts included, yet. Static fonts do not need to have a STAT table. It is only recommended by Microsoft, not required.
More infos here:
https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/typography/opentype/spec/stat

Titillium Web ExtraLight Regular (TitilliumWeb-ExtraLight.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'TitilliumWeb-ExtraLight', Everything looks good.

Titillium Web ExtraLight Regular (TitilliumWeb-ExtraLight.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Titillium Web' + 'Space' + NID 17 'ExtraLight' = NID 1 'Titillium Web ExtraLight'.

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Titillium Web' + 'Space' + NID 17 'ExtraLight Italic' = NID 1 'Titillium Web ExtraLight' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Titillium Web Light Regular (TitilliumWeb-Light.ttf)

name

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'TitilliumWeb-Light', Everything looks good.

Titillium Web Light Regular (TitilliumWeb-Light.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Titillium Web' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Light' = NID 1 'Titillium Web Light'.

Pass

Titillium Web Light Italic (TitilliumWeb-LightItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Titillium Web' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Light Italic' = NID 1 'Titillium Web Light' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Mac NID 6

, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'TitilliumWeb-Italic', Everything looks good.

Titillium Web SemiBold Regular (TitilliumWeb-SemiBold.ttf)

name

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'TitilliumWeb-SemiBold', Everything looks good.

Pass

Titillium Web SemiBold Regular (TitilliumWeb-SemiBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'TitilliumWeb-SemiBold', Everything looks good.

Titillium Web SemiBold Regular (TitilliumWeb-SemiBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Titillium Web' + 'Space' + NID 17 'SemiBold' = NID 1 'Titillium Web SemiBold'.

NID 6 is 'TitilliumWeb-SemiBoldItalic', Everything looks good.

Titillium Web SemiBold Italic (TitilliumWeb-SemiBoldItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Titillium Web' + 'Space' + NID 17 'SemiBold Italic' = NID 1 'Titillium Web SemiBold' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Mac NID 6

NID 6 is 'TitilliumWeb-Bold', Everything looks good.

Titillium Web Bold Italic (TitilliumWeb-BoldItalic.ttf)

name

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'TitilliumWeb-BoldItalic', Everything looks good.

Titillium Web Black Regular (TitilliumWeb-Black.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Titillium Web' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Black' = NID 1 'Titillium Web Black'.
